<% provide( :title, 'Problem 1' ) %>

<div class = "center hero-unit" >
  <h1>Problem 1</h1>
  If we list all the natural numbers below 10 that are multiples of 3 or 5, 
  we get 3, 5, 6 and 9.<br>
  The sum of these multiples is 23.

  <h2>Find the sum of all the multiples of 3 or 5 below 1000.</h2>
  <%= form_tag( { :controller => 'static_pages', :action => 'problem1' }, 
    :method => 'get' ) do %>
    <%= text_field_tag( :max, 'max number' ) %><br>
  <% end %>
  <% if (@answer > 0) %>
    Sum of Multiples: <%= @answer %>
  <% end %>
</div>
